text: The men's 3 metre springboard diving competition at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro was held on 15 and 16 August at the Maria Lenk Aquatic Center in Barra da Tijuca. == Format == The competition was held in three rounds: * Preliminary round: All 29 divers perform six dives; the top 18 divers advance to the semi-final. * Semi-final: The 18 divers perform six dives; the scores of the qualifications are erased and the top 12 divers advance to the final. * Final: The 12 divers perform six dives; the semi-final scores are erased and the top three divers win the gold, silver and bronze medals accordingly. == Schedule == All times are Brasília time (UTC−3) {| class="wikitable" !Date !Time !Round |- |Monday, 15 August 2016 |15:15 |Preliminary |- |Tuesday, 16 August 2016 |10:00
